OL,4,Cquoted using vulgar term about gay men
OL,6,FOn Monday Italian media quoted unnamed
OL,7,FItalian bishops in reporting that
OL,8,FFrancis jokingly used the term
OL,9,F"f*****tness" while speaking in
OL,10,FItalian during the encounter.
